sequenceDiagram
    actor U as Utilisateur
    participant FE as Angular Frontend
    participant API as ReviewController
    participant SVC as ReviewService
    participant MONGO as MongoDB (estore.reviews)

    U->>FE: Soumet un avis (note + commentaire)
    FE->>API: POST /api/reviews\n{productId, rating, comment}\n(Authorization: Bearer JWT)
    API->>API: @PreAuthorize("isAuthenticated()")
    alt Token JWT absent ou invalide
        API-->>FE: 401 Unauthorized
        FE-->>U: Redirection vers login
    else Token valide
        API->>SVC: create(reviewRequest, currentUser)
        SVC->>MONGO: save(Review{productId, userId,\n authorName, rating, comment,\n createdAt})
        alt MongoDB disponible
            MONGO-->>SVC: Review document (id auto-généré)
            SVC-->>API: ReviewResponse
            API-->>FE: 201 Created + ReviewResponse
            FE-->>U: Avis publié — liste mise à jour
        else MongoDB indisponible
            MONGO-->>SVC: Exception connexion
            SVC-->>API: 503 Service Unavailable
            API-->>FE: 503
            FE-->>U: Erreur — service temporairement indisponible
        end
    end

    Note over FE,MONGO: La lecture des avis (GET /api/reviews/product/{id})\nest publique — aucun token requis
